                  } text-sm`}>
                    {msg.text}
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>

            <div className="p-2 bg-white rounded-bubble border border-border flex items-center space-x-2 shadow-xl">
              <input 
                type="text" 
                value={inputValue}
                onChange={(e) => setInputValue(e.target.value)}
                onKeyDown={(e) => e.key === 'Enter' && handleSendMessage()}
                placeholder="Ask about pool hours, tee times..." 
